data.description: Waterfront home in Evergreen addition! Right in the heart of New Market Square you'll have all the amenities just down the street. This home offers 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Interior updates include new carpet, luxury vinyl plank, new paint, lighting and new kitchen appliances!! The master bedroom is huge with deck access and the en-suite has a separate tub & shower along with a large walk in closet. You'll always feel connected with family and guests on the main floor living, dining and kitchen area, its very open and a great place to gather. In the lower level you have a fireplace and a projector screen that compliment the family room as well as two additional bedrooms and a full bath, this is also a walk-out basement!  On the deck you have tons of space to entertain and amazing lake views! There is a sidewalk from the back gate that wraps around the lake and connects to a playground area. Roof was installed in 2018 and irrigation well in 2019.
